Implementation for blLegRoast.
This is a fork of the original LegRoast code, taken from https://github.com/WardBeullens/LegRoast

To test the blinding,
    make blindtest
    ./blindtest

To test the original LegRoast code for comparison:
    make test
    ./test


Tested on Ubuntu 18.04.4 LTS
required packages:
gcc
xsltproc
libssl-dev
libgmp-dev
